{
  "stem": "512.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But it healed up after several years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It healed up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "After digging the ditches, then in the spring, they started selecting girls to work for the farmers in the fields.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was never among the lucky ones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "At least they got fed there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You know, from work we were not afraid, but for hunger was the-- hunger was the most horrible, horrible thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They got fed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The farmer fed them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So the girls would say that they looked so bewildered.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They put out the food, and they-- the girls start grabbing it and putting it into their bosoms and-- they just couldn't understand that they'll bring you more.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Don't grab from the table.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So the next day, they would send another group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I was never-- we were never-- not my sister, not me, were ever lucky to be selected.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But here and there there was a Nazi with humanity in him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Like she would look at my sister.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "She was so small and fragile [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that she would call her over and give her a little bit leftover of her food, shared with me.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So-- and then one day they just announced for us that they had, from the Red Cross, they received orders.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They're going to take us to Sweden on a boat, and we're all going to be liberated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So the happiness was beyond words.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They told us, all you can take is-- we didn't have anything what to take-- but whoever wants to take their bowl, you know, for in case somewhere somebody is going to be kind enough to serve us some food.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We took the bowl with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Again, they put us into cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were travelling.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
